title: San Francisco board eyes measures on immigrant sanctuary
text: SAN FRANCISCO (AP) - San Francisco supervisors will try Tuesday to decide whether to continue a policy that prevents cooperation with federal immigration officials that gained attention when a man in the country illegally killed a woman on a city pier.
